One big down side for me was that we were unable to have the use of an iron in the room as the hotel only offer an ironing service.	You need to use their ironing service.	Approx 8 Euros for washing and ironing a single shirt.	There are laundry facilities available but at high prices.	I only decided to write this review to point out that if you need to iron your clothes, you can't have an iron or ironing board brought to your room.	There is a business center downstairs with two computers and one printer, which would come in handy if you wanted to print out your boarding passes.